the visitor can visit the objects/classes of ANY types
The new operation is created by adding a visitor-subclass to the hierarchy of visitor classes
compared to the previous illustration, this is simply a different arrangement of elements, so that you can compare it to the acyclic visitor and the object-extension pattern
